RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT CONTRACT_REF_NO,LATEST_VERSION_NO,COUNTERPARTY,PRODUCT_TYPE,AUTH_STATUS FROM oltbs_contract where MODULE_CODE = 'LB' AND PRODUCT_TYPE IN ('C') AND CONTRACT_STATUS NOT IN ('L', 'V') AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM smvws_user_branches b WHERE b.User_id = global.user_id AND b.Branch_code = oltbs_contract.branch) AND BRANCH=global.current_branch ORDER BY CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT distinct c.ccy_code, c.ccy_name FROM cytms_ccy_defn c, lbtbs_borrower_ccy l WHERE c.ccy_code = l.ccy AND l.contract_ref_no = ? AND l.ccy not in (SELECT currency FROM LbTB_PART_SETTLE_CURR_DET_TEMP a WHERE a.contract_ref_no = ? AND a.participant = ?)

SELECT ssi_mnemonic, counterparty, NVL((SELECT customer_name1 FROM oltms_customer WHERE customer_no = a.counterparty),DECODE(counterparty, 'ALL', 'ALL CUSTOMERS')), currency, product_code, settlement_seq_no, module, branch, pay_ac_branch, pay_account, pay_account_ccy, recv_ac_branch, recv_account, recv_account_ccy FROM OLTM_INSTR a WHERE counterparty IN (?,'ALL') AND Currency IN (?,'*.*') AND branch IN (sypks_utils.get_branch(?), 'ALL') AND module IN ('LP','AL') AND product_code IN (sypks_utils.get_product(?),'ALL') AND a.record_stat = 'O' AND a.auth_stat = 'A' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM olvws_PROD_ACNT_Access X WHERE (PAY_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO or RECV_ACCOUNT = X.AC_GL_NO) AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = sypks_utils.get_product(?))

select a.entity, a.entity_name, a.entity_type from oltms_customer_entity_details a where a.customer_no = ? and a.entity not in (select entity_id from oltbs_contract_entity_temp b where b.contract_ref_no = ? and b.customer_no = a.customer_no and b.entity_id = a.entity and b.contract_type IN ('TR', 'DR'))

SELECT A.COUNTERPARTY, C.CUSTOMER_NAME1 as CUST_NAME FROM LBTBS_PART_PROC_STAT A ,OLTBS_CONTRACT B,OLTMS_CUSTOMER C WHERE A.BORROWER_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.COUNTERPARTY = C.CUSTOMER_NO AND A.BORROWER_REF_NO = ?
